The paper focuses on privacy concerns in IoT systems and proposes a privacy-by-design framework for assessing existing applications and middleware platforms. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), software engineering (cs.SE), cybernetics (cs.CY), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
